company_name: MOBY DICK FISCH, GEFLÜGEL UND DELIKATESSEN HANDELS GMBH
information: The company MOBY DICK FISCH, GEFLÜGEL UND DELIKATESSEN HANDELS GMBH, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1977, which operates in the Finishing work industry. It also operates in the Gastronomic specialties, and Fish industries. It is based in München, Germany.
